public class MethodList
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Composite
implements iMenuWidget, MethodService.MethodServiceHandler, ISearchController

This Class instantiates the MethodList Service and converts the corresponding list of POJO data classes (pojoMethod) into stacks in a stack panel. NB: Each Stack has a MethodMenuItem widget which allows for Editing and Cloning of Methods NB2: A DragEvent is used to alert a presenter that data has been selected

This class is a Member of the MethodBuilder package which in included in the Monbulk project
